WHAT IS THIS THING?
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
HIT TILES 2 SPECIAL EDITION is a game based on the well-known oriental game
called Shanghai. It consists of 15 levels, each one featuring a screen made
up of 120 tiles placed in piles up to 4 high. In every screen there are 4 of
each tile. The aim of the game is to remove all of the tiles from the screen.
The main and only rule you have to keep in mind is this: You can only remove
2 equals tiles at a time ad both must have an empty place on either the left
or the right hand side.



